name: Husbant
description: Husbant is here to make memecoins great again. Launched stealth with no presale, zero taxes, LP burnt and contract renounced, SUPPORT OF THE COMMUNITY You can contribute to the success of Husbant by shilling our links to your Twitter, Discord or Telegram, showing support in our telegram group and engaging with our social media posts ensuring max exposure. If you have any creative ideas to help build and promote Husbant please feel free to share it with us. Being a memecoin doesn’t mean we won’t have utilities. Our developers will develop some fun and useful tools for its community members as we continue to BUIDL! Our main goal is to make sure everyone has access to our utilities, so we build it with scalability in mind. What’s next for your Husbant? Community engagement, support, and growth are the main focus of Husbant and will continue to be going forward. Additionally, Husbant plans to deploy multiple community rewards programs such as buy backs, fee sharing, incentivized task completion, and more. Husbant can be used in upcoming community rewards programs, as a medium of exchange, and a store of value.
